overview: Ah, the age-old dilemma, do you date someone for their mind or their looks? In episode 16, our gals wrestle with this riddle -and their current squeezes! Annie's new galpal is intellectually stimulating...but lacking between the sheets. Tori's latest lover is good at the grind -but she longs for Chad's mental challenges! Monica discovers a new depth of shallowness with ex-enemy Angie! And Lindsey wonders why can't have both brains and beauty!
title: Naked Hollywood 16: Brains Or Beauty
